HEADWORD: Foreskirt
<hw>Fore"skirt`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The front skirt of
a garment, in distinction from the <contr>train</contr>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Honor's train⟦br⟧
Is longer than his <qex>foreskirt</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Foreslack</ent>⟦br⟧
